    "id": "quantitative-primer-problem-029",
    "titleEn": "Question 29 - a and b, where a < b, and a measuring apparatus with a variance of σ2, due to measurement error",
    "titleZh": "Question 29 - a and b, where a < b, and a measuring apparatus with a variance of σ2, due to measurement error",
    "category": "statistics",
